(27758, 'Svr sunsecure spf 50+ hydrating milk 100 ml', 'اس في ار صنسيكيور 50+ هيدرايتنج ميلك 100مل', '', '399', '', 'Svr laboratoire dermatologique > biotech egypt', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Sunblock', '100 ml', 'use before exposing the skin to sunlight apply evenly to the face. re-apply regularly.', '', '', 841, '2022-07-19', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(2432, 'Gastrotidine 20 mg/2ml 3 i.m./i.v. amps', 'جاستروتيدين 20مجم/2مل 3 أمبولات', '37.5', '54', 'Famotidine', 'Chemipharm', 'Amp', 'أمبول', 'للحموضة وقرحة المعدة', 'H2 blocker peptic ulcer hyperacidity', '20 mg', 'Famotidine is indicated in pediatric and adult patients (with the bodyweight of 40 kg and above) for the management of active duodenal ulcer (DU), active gastric ulcer, symptomatic non-erosive gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD), and erosive esophagitis due to GERD, diagnosed by biopsy.[L11139]
It is also indicated in adult patients for the treatment of pathological hypersecretory conditions (e.g., Zollinger-Ellison Syndrome, multiple endocrine neoplasias) and reduction of the risk of DU recurrence.[L11139]
